What will you do:

Collaborate with cross-functional teams to integrate machine learning models into products and services;
Deploy, monitor, and maintain machine learning models in production environments;
Manage and improve the infrastructure and tooling to accelerate model development and experimentation;
Develop backend services (e.g., REST APIs) that expose ML capabilities, ensuring scalability and efficiency in production environments;
