Experience with Kubernetes (ideally AKS);
Prior experience speeding up and reducing GPU memory requirements for large deep learning models during training and inference (Nvidia Triton Server);
Experience creating LLM-based agents and workflows (Langchain);
Experience with event-driven architectures and messaging systems like Kafka, RabbitMQ.




