PhD in Computer Science, Machine Learning, or related field;
5+ years of experience in AI/ML in industry with demonstrable technical contributions;
Publication record or demonstrable research output in machine learning or AI;
Deep technical expertise in GenAI (LLMs, generative models, speech, etc.);
Experience leading technical teams through complex research challenges in fast-paced, product-focused environments;
