Good coding skills in Python and familiarity with modern ML frameworks (PyTorch, TensorFlow, etc.);
Experience with the full ML lifecycle, from ideation to deployment;
Strong communication skills with the ability to explain complex technical concepts to diverse audiences;
Strong product sense and impeccable ability to do research with strong alignment towards business objectives



